folios.text:
ffar noffgot may my dic
 fuyel &c feiligen grubes
 &c ift ein aler namenmel
 feyn gemachf nber &ab geflig
 fynb &o mynper gere gerwra
 got vnd monpf my gtegen
 yt nnd &o noy, wferpandly
 my &cm eritten tag noy
 dem tod
 &c ift my tor &c8 tempel8
 &o ift ein locg vnd ftat &un
 fi cin, flein, ftan, &o fpang
 niper gere &g were &ab mttel
 fec owch
 &f me notgeteftinbay fen&8 dic
 Dic bilgerftet ofwenbig &c8
 tempel8 my &aw ftat
 &f &ab guo &c8 &nffg vndf
